author: RTÉ News
title: Germany marks third day of new infections accelerating
description: Germany's confirmed coronavirus cases increased by 2,352 to 148,046, marking a third consecutive day of new infections accelerating.
content:
Germany's confirmed coronavirus cases increased by 2,352 to 148,046, data from the Robert Koch Institute (RKI) for infectious diseases showed on Thursday, marking a third consecutive day of new infections accelerating.
